{
  "stem": "11801.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were only, as far as I knew, six or seven Jewish children in the orphanage, and out of, you know, 350 or so, it didn't make a great impact on the amount of food that we received, which was very small.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] no one ever mentioned it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But going to school, leaving-- leaving the confines of the orphanage became very dangerous, and we were no longer allowed to do that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the-- the orphanage, the grounds were very spacious.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were allowed to wander around the grounds.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Not that we did that, because we didn't see much point.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were kept busy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, if you live with 60 other children, there's always a lot to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so we were kept busy doing, basically, chores.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Our education stopped altogether.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were advised to do homework with the other children, which was really not very productive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I never did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I just didn't find that a way of learning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And books were not readily available.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I think I read maybe two or three books during those years, because we didn't have books.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We did-- we were not given the opportunity to go to libraries.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We didn't have-- I'm not sure that libraries existed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I'm sure they existed in a town, but the orphanage was not really focused on education.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was focused on, at least, feeding and housing children for a while.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Very few were there as long as I was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was another problem.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You tried not to get too attached to anybody because you knew they would leave.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And so it was dangerous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Again, for me, it was another sign that I had to depend only on myself.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
